short.ar: Put Bacon هي لعبة أركيد ممتعة حيث نحاول رمي Bacon يسارًا من أعلى في سلة المهملات باستخدام المقلاة.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Put Bacon is a fun arcade game where we try to throw the Bacon left from above into the Trash with a pan.
The game has Bacon dropped from above. We carefully drop this Bacon, bounce it off the pan, and try to throw it away. As we throw the Pastrami in the Trash, we complete the sections. By completing the chapters, we unlock new chapters and continue the game. Throw the Pastrami in the Trash is a fun skill game designed for those who love arcade games.

To swipe Install this extension to play the Put Bacon Game or offline with no additional downloads and no ads.
